quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  10,90,"Netusomosa abaana ba Israil ennyanja olwo ne Firawo n'abawondera n'amagyege mu ngeri ey'obulabe n’obulumbaganyi, okutuusa lwe yatuukibwako okuzikirira mu mazzi olwo naagamba nti: nzikirizza nti mazima ddala tewali Katonda asinzibwa mu butuufu okugyako oyo abaana ba Israil gwe bakkiriza era nze ndi mu basiramuse"
  10,91,(Firawo naagambibwa nti kati olwo okkiriza) so nga wajeema dda n'obeera mu boonoonyi
  10,92,"Kale nno olwa leero tujja kukuwonya (kukuuma) omulambogwo (guleme kuvunda) olyoke obeere eky'okulabirako eri abalijja oluvanyumalwo, mazima abantu abasinga obungi tebafaayo (kwegasa na bubonero bwaffe)"
  10,93,"Mazima twasenza abaana ba Israil mu kifo e kirungi ekyesiimisa netubagabirira mu bigabwa ebirungi, nebataba na njawukana (mu ddiini) okutuusa okumanya lwe kwabajjira (nti Nabbi Muhammad ajja kujja nga mubaka wa Katonda) mazima Katonda agenda kulamula wakati wa bwe ku lunaku lw'enkomerero mu ekyo kye baali baawukanamu"
  10,94,"Bwoba nga olimu okubuusabuusa (Ggwe Muhammad) ku ebyo bye twassa gyoli buuza abo abaasoma e kitabo oluberyeberyelwo, ddala amazima gakujjidde okuva ewa Mukama omulabiriziwo kale togeza nga n'obeera mu babuusabuusa"
  10,95,Era ddala tobeeranga mu abo abalimbisa e bigambo bya Katonda n'obeera mu bafaafaganirwa
  10,96,Mazima abo abaakakatako ekigambo kya Mukama omulabiriziwo tebagenda kukkiriza
  10,97,Nebwebanajjirwa buli kabonero okutuusa lwe baliraba e bibonerezo ebiruma
  10,98,Tewali bantu ba kitundu bakkiriza obukkiriza bwa bwe nebubagasa okugyako abantu ba Yunusu anti bwe bakkiriza twabaggyako ebibonerezo ebiswaza mu bulamu buno obw'ensi netubeeyagaza okutuusa ku ntuuko zaabwe
  10,99,"Singa Mukama omulabiriziwo yayagala abantu abali mu nsi bandikkirizza bonna, kaakati ggwe oyagala kukaka bantu bonna babeere bakkiriza"
  10,100,"Tewali muntu ayinza kukikkiriza okugyako ng’akkiriza lwa kwagala kwa Katonda, era Katonda assa ekibi ku abo abatategeera"
  10,101,"Bagambe nti: mwetegereze ebiri mu ggulu (omusanvu) n'ensi naye obubonero n'okutiisa tebigasa bantu batakkiriza"
  10,102,"Abaffe balina kye balindirira mpozzi ekifaananako ne nnaku zaabo abaabakulembera., bagambe nti: mulindirire nange ndi wamu na mmwe mu balindirira"
  10,103,Oluvanyuma ne tuwonya (ne tutaasa) ababaka baffe n'abo abakkiriza bwe tutyo nno bulijjo kikakafu kuffe okutaasa abakkiriza
  10,104,"Bagambe nti: abange mmwe abantu bwe muba nga mulina okubuusabuusa mu ddiini yange (mukitegeere nti) sisinza abo be musinza nemuva ku Katonda, wabula nsinza Katonda oyo abatta ,era nnalagirwa mbeere mu bakkiriza"
  10,105,Era tereera mu ddiini ya Katonda n'goli mwesimbu era ddala tobeeranga mu bagatta e bintu e birala ku Katonda
  10,106,Tolekanga Katonda n'osaba e kintu e kirala ekyo ekitakugasa era ekitayinza kukutuusako kabi naye bwonookikola mazima ddala ggwe olwo nno onoobeera mu abo abeeyisa obubi
  10,107,"Singa Mukama Katonda akutuusaako ekibi tewali ayinza kukikuggyako okugyako yye, ate singa aba akwagalizza kirungi teri ayinza kuzzaayo birungibye, abifunyisa oyo gwaba ayagadde mu baddube, era yye bulijjo ye musonyiyi, omusaasizi owa nnamaddala"
  10,108,"Bagambe (Ggwe Muhammad) nti; abange mmwe abantu amazima gabajjidde okuva ewa Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe oyo yenna alungama aba yeelungamidde, ate oyo abula okubulakwe kukosa yye. Nze siri mukuumi ku mmwe"
  10,109,"Era goberera ebyo ebitumwa gyoli era ogumiikirize okutuusa Katonda lwa naasalawo, anti bulijjo yye yaasinga abasalawo bonna"
  11,1,"Alif Laam Raa, ekitabo kino e bigambo by'akyo byasengekebwa oluvanyuma nebinnyonnyolwa mu bujjuvu okuva ewa Katonda akola buli kintu ng’asinziira ku nsonga ng’ate amanyi mu bujjuvu buli kintu"
  11,2,Kitegeeza abantu nti temusinzanga kintu kyonna wabula Katonda yekka mazima nze gye muli ndi mutiisa (ku bibonerezo bye) era omusanyusa (olw'emperaye eri abalongoosa)
  11,3,"(Era kibagamba) nti mwegayirire Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe era mumwenenyeze olwo nno ajja kubeeyagaza olweyagaza olulungi okutuusa ku kiseera ekigere era buli oyo yenna ateekeddwa okufuna obulungi agenda kumuwa obulungibwe, naye bwe muva ku ekyo mazima nze mbatiirira ebibonerezo by'olunaku oluzibu"
  11,4,Eri Katonda y'eri obuddo bwa mmwe ate yye nga bulijjo muyinza ku buli kintu
  11,5,"Abange mazima bbo (abatakkiriza) bakweka ebifuba byabwe babe nga beekweka Katonda, abange (mukimanye nti) ne mu kiseera webeebikkira engoye zaabwe Katonda amanya ebyo bye bakweka ne bye boolesa, anti mazima yye amanyidde ddala ebiri mu bifuba"